name: multio
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "multio" %}
{% set version = "0.2.5" %}

package:
  name: "{{ name|lower }}"
  version: "{{ version }}"

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/{{ name }}-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: fdcd9bd48d053da9f44b1ca56c2f7cf0902d4eb76b41cf16b684166d7180f79f

build:
  noarch: python
  number: 0
  script: "{{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . --no-deps --ignore-installed --no-cache-dir -vvv "

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.5
  run:
    - python >=3.5

test:
  imports:
    - multio

about:
  home: https://github.com/theelous3/multio
  license: MIT
  license_family: MIT
  license_file: '{{ environ["RECIPE_DIR"] }}/LICENCE.txt' 
  summary: multio - an unified async library for curio and trio

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - CJ-Wright
